    {
        "content": "<p>That what the discharger is for, <code>simp (disch:=assumption)</code> You can specify a tactic to discharge assumptions for conditional simp theorems. <code>assumption</code> should be enough in this case.</p>\n<p><code>simp +contextual</code> should work after <code>revert ha</code> too</p>\n<p>I'm on the phone and I didn't test it so hopefully it works.<br>\n(Btw I see you are struggling with jetlag too <span aria-label=\"grinning face with smiling eyes\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f601\" role=\"img\" title=\"grinning face with smiling eyes\">:grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes:</span> )</p>",
